 le 5 avril 1357, à Lochawe, Argyll, Écosse, à l’âge de 29 ans, et a été enterrée à Lochawe, Argyll, Écosse."},"de":{"1328–5 April 1357":"1328–5. April 1357","1328–1357":"1328–1357","1330–1380":"1330–1380","1345–1420":"1345–1420","1350–Male":"1350–Verstorben","1285–1353":"1285–1353","1306–Female":"1306–Verstorben","5 April 1357":"5. April 1357","1330":"1330","1285":"1285","1350":"1350","1380":"1380","before 1328":"vor 1328","1357":"1357","1345":"1345","1420":"1420","1353":"1353","about 1345":"um 1345","January 1345":"Januar 1345","1328":"1328","1306":"1306","Glenorchy, Argyll, Scotland":"Glenorchy, Argyll, Scotland","Lochgoilhead, Argyll, Scotland":"Lochgoilhead, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland","Lochawe, Argyll, Scotland":"Lochawe, Argyll, Scotland","lifeSummary":"Als Mariota Campbell 1328 in Glenorchy, Argyll, Scotland geboren wurde, war ihr Vater Iain Campbell Of Ardscotnish 43 und ihre Mutter Mariata MacGregor 22. Sie hat um 1345 in Argyll, Scotland John Campbell geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn und 1 Tochter. Sie starb am 5. April 1357 im Alter von 29 Jahren in Lochawe, Argyll, Scotland und wurde in Lochawe, Argyll, Scotland begraben."},"ht":{"1328–5 April 1357":"1328–5 April 1357","1328–1357":"1328–1357","1330–1380":"1330–1380","1345–1420":"1345–1420","1350–Male":"1350–Desede","1285–1353":"1285–1353","1306–Female":"1306–Desede","5 April 1357":"5 April 1357","1330":"1330","1285":"1285","1350":"1350","1380":"1380","before 1328":"before 1328","1357":"1357","1345":"1345","1420":"1420","1353":"1353","about 1345":"about 1345","January 1345":"January 1345","1328":"1328","1306":"1306","Glenorchy, Argyll, Scotland":"Glenorchy, Argyll, Scotland","Lochgoilhead, Argyll, Scotland":"Lochgoilhead, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland","Lochawe, Argyll, Scotland":"Lochawe, Argyll, Scotland"},"hu":{"1328–5 April 1357":"1328–1357. április 5.","1328–1357":"1328–1357","1330–1380":"1330–13